title: Neutrogena MoistureShine Lip Gloss, Berry Fit 400
description: Neutrogena MoistureShine Gloss has silky, sheer color that glides onto lips, leaving them feeling pampered, soft and ultra-smooth. The super conditioning formula with a triple berry antioxidant complex--including Acai, Goji and Aronia berries--actually improves the healthy look, softness and smoothness of your lips over time. From soft neutrals to blushing pinks, shimmering mauves to rich plums, a single swipe of the wand applies a feather-light coat of glossy color that's not sticky or tacky.

title: Bvlgari Aqua By Bvlgari For Men. Eau De Toilette Spray 1.7 Ounces
description: When applying any fragrance please consider that there are several factors which can affect the natural smell of your skin and, in turn, the way a scent smells on you.  For instance, your mood, stress level, age, body chemistry, diet, and current medications may all alter the scents you wear.  Similarly, factor such as dry or oily skin can even affect the amount of time a fragrance will last after being applied

title: MASH Crystal Glass Nail File (Full Sized)
description: Ordinary nail files? NO THANK YOU!Take a close look at your fingernails. Are they strong and healthy looking? Or do you see ridges, dents, or areas of unusual shape? It's time for some TLC ladies and gentleman! Many less than desirable nail conditions can be avoided through proper fingernail care, which is why we owe the makers at MASH a pat on the back. With the Crystal Glass Nail , you will be on the road to recovery in no time!

title: Nivea Body Crème Jar, 6.8 oz (Pack Of 3)
description: Enjoy the rich luxurious sensation of Nivea Creme while you moisturize your skin. Its clinically proven formula helps your skin stay soft and supple all day long. Can be used all over the body, and best for rough spots such as knees, feet, elbows and hands. Dermatologically tested and approved
